title: Ep. 123 "Stop Giving Mixed Signals!!!"
description: This week we're talking about the mixed signals we give and get.  Why are you promising to help but when somebody asks for a little couch, it's a problem????  If I tell you I want a relationship, but not WITH YOU, what part of that is left up for interpretation??  We get them, we give them, now let's talk about them.
